We are a traditional Irish pub and do not take reservations. Seating is first come, first serve and you order at the bar.
We do *not* take reservations for parties during the months of January-March as this is our busy season. After those months, in order to book a party upstairs your party must have at least 40+ people to book seating.
We do now require a small
deposit to book any party.
All band inquires, please email at:
theraypg3@gmail.com
